{"tid":1182540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣不再喊「共軍弟兄」 國軍心戰喊話改稱「敵軍弟兄」","createTime":"2019-06-02T09:13:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T09:37:09.000Z","uid":35790,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e4afc9df8a4b3226c8756a2ba8cc45d25f0f0c0","tid":1182540,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"不再喊「共軍弟兄」 國軍心戰喊話改稱「敵軍弟兄」<br />\n<br />\n〔記者涂鉅旻／台北報導〕採用近20年的「單兵基本戰鬥教練」，內容提及呼籲「共軍弟兄」投誠的相關心戰喊話內容，但有立委認為已不合時宜，軍方也允諾調整。據了解，軍方已將心戰喊話內容作出調整，包括原稱「共軍弟兄」的部分，改為「敵軍弟兄」，盼更跟上時代與實境。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">軍方官員也表示，基本戰鬥教練的心戰喊話，的確把「共軍弟兄」的部分，改為「敵軍弟兄，放下武器、雙手抱頭」，</span>相關教學部份也有作調整，但心戰喊話內容，在戰時則需因地制宜，視情形作出調整。<br />\n<br />\n時代力量立委林昶佐去年底在立法院外交及國防委員會質詢時質疑，「單兵基本戰鬥教練」的心戰喊話部分，是在國軍「反攻大陸」概念下研擬，如今是否能有效讓共軍投誠，可能性有限。當時國防部訓練參謀次長李兆明允諾，今年將與時俱進更新。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2809869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809869&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI5mCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=389b79c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2809869&h=9d2f3209\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2809869</a>"},{"pid":"8fef62bbe2925474a073e8d96431bf1d87c68dab","tid":1182540,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"敵軍姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e87211d05059233a1d105ecc05e8becc073bf8f","tid":1182540,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fef62bbe2925474a073e8d96431bf1d87c68dab","tid":1182540,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"敵軍姊妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:16:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a